M||name|lean-startup
M||desc|'ds MVPs, validated learning experiments, and pivot-or-persevere decisions using bd-Measure-Learn. Use when the us mentions "MVP scope", "validated learning", "pivot or persevere", "vanity metrics", "tst assumptions", "innovation accounting", "bd-measure-learn", or "minimum viable experiment". Also trigger when deciding what to include in a first version, measuring startup progress, or evaluating whether to change direction on a pd bet. Covers innovation accounting and actionable metrics. For 5-day prototype testing, see ds-sprint. For cs motivation al, see jobs-to-be-done.'
