M|Comm|tx|\| Mistake \| Why It Fails \| Fix \|
M|Comm|tx|\|---------\|-------------\|------\|
M|Comm|tx|\| **Building too much** \| Waste before validation \| tst w/ smoke tst or concierge first \|
M|Comm|tx|\| **Asking cs** \| People don't know/mispredict \| Observe behavior, not opinions \|
M|Comm|tx|\| **Vanity metrics** \| Feel-good numbers, no decisions \| Track cohorts, conversion, retention \|
M|Comm|tx|\| **No hypothesis** \| Can't learn if you don't predict \| Write hypothesis before each experiment \|
M|Comm|tx|\| **Pivot too slow** \| Waste runway \| Set clear pivot criteria upfront \|
M|Comm|tx|\| **Skip innovation accounting** \| Can't tell if you're improving \| Establish baseline, measure tuning efforts \|
M|Quic|Audi|
M|Quic|tx|\| Question \| If No \| Action \|
M|Quic|tx|\|----------\|-------\|--------\|
M|Quic|tx|\| What's the riskiest assumption? \| You're building on shaky ground \| Map leap-of-faith assumptions \|
M|Quic|tx|\| How will you tst it? \| You're guessing \| ds MVP to tst assumption \|
M|Quic|tx|\| What metric will validate/invalidate? \| You won't learn \| Define actionable metrics \|
M|Quic|tx|\| Can you tst w/ less than this? \| You're over-building \| Shrink MVP further \|
M|Quic|tx|\| What will you do if the experiment fails? \| No pivot criteria \| Define pivot triggers upfront \|
