M|Abou|tx|**Eric Ries** is an entrepreneur and author best known for developing the Lean Startup methodology. He was co-founder and CTO of IMVU, where he pioneered continuous dpl and cs dv practices that became the foundation of Lean Startup. *The Lean Startup* has been translated into over 30 languages and has influenced startup culture worldwide. Ries is also the creator of the Long-Term Stock Exchange (LTSE), a new stock exchange designed for companies focused on long-term value creation.